# wandb job

## 

​

Usage
    
    
    job [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...
    

## 

​

Description

Commands for managing and viewing W&B jobs.

## 

​

Subcommands

Command| Description  
---|---  
`wandb job create`| Create a job from a source, without a wandb run.  
`wandb job describe`| Describe a launch job. Provide the launch job in the form  
`wandb job list`| List jobs in a project.  
  
